structure.unit: LICENSING OF MOTOR VEHICLES, OPERATORS, AND TRAILERS

law.history: Repealed 2002 Ky. Acts ch. 264, sec. 10, effective July 15, 2002. -- Amended 1996 Ky. Acts ch. 185, sec. 2, effective July 15, 1996. -- Amended 1978 Ky. Acts ch. 155, sec. 41, effective June 17, 1978. -- Created 1974 Ky. Acts ch. 124, sec. 3.
